							<p>Micro content is pics and videos that is designed specifically for different social media platforms.</p>

							<p>All of our micro content include an interactive part to inspire, teach or entertain guests.</p>

							<p>Examples: Quotes, facts, infographics, short video clips, interviews, photo series, customer content creation, brand inspired content, event recaps, etc.</p>
						</div>


					</div>

					<div class="image-part1">
						<%= image_tag 'yellowbike-shape.svg', :class => "bikeimage" %>
					</div>


			</div>

