					<div class="image-part1">
						<%= image_tag 'bike-shape.svg', :class => "bikeimage2" %>
					</div>

					<div class="microsite-info">
						<div class="microsite-title">Interactive Microsite</div>

						<div class="microsite-para">
							<p>We provide microsites that are great to bring customers to your product or service.  We provide ways to gain more info from customers and opportunity to gain sales and grow leads.</p>

							<p>A micorsite is basically a mini site outside your primary website to promote a campaign, connect to new markets or showcase new products.</p>

							<p>All of our microsites include an interactive part to inspire, teach or entertain guests.</p>

							<p>Examples: Quizzes, surveys, games, contests, giveaways, event participation, 
							meme/social media generator, interative infographics, etc.</p>

						</div>


					</div>


